data.description: Absolutely Stunning Home lots of Upgrades*2 Bedroom  3rd floor Highrise Across the street from New F-1 Las Vegas site, Close to Raider stadium *walking distance to all the FUN the STRIP can offer. Upgraded Kitchen custom cabinets Granite Countertops, Large Terrace upgraded flooring throughout, 24-7 security guard and cameras, Pool, Sauna, Gym,Tennis courts, basketball courts,BBQ area,Club house and Exercise Room. Underground Parking Electric Gates and Keypad w/2 spaces. Solar Screens  New owner will also have a Storage unit !!
